apiConfig._comment: Coingecko API url that is used to get the price of specified tokens in USD.

caching._comment: Numbers are in seconds. 86400 seconds = 1 day. 3600 seconds = 1 hour. 60 seconds = 1 minute.

tokenAddresses._comment: Token addresses referencing the Solana mainnet. These are used to look up token prices from specific DEXs or markets.

StarAtlastokenAddresses._comment: Token addresses referencing the Star Atlas items mint addresses. These are used to look up token specific data.
